				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Provide examples for the tool in an example class that cover: (1) success case(s), (2) missing arguments, and (3) error/missing resources. Provide examples for any domain objects that get created that verify that they are created ok, and that they serialize ok to JSON. Run the examples and report results. "
			},
