					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "Place the tool class in the package {{gtPackage:Gt4LlmCore}} and the example classes in the package {{gtPackage:Gt4LlmCore-Examples}} . Learn more about the patterns for creating LLM tools from related classes in these packages."
